* TemporaryOahSystem#diabetes-mellitus "% of deaths due to Diabetes Mellitus"
* TemporaryOahSystem#endocrine-nutritional-metabolic "% of deaths due to endocrine, nutritional and metabolic diseases"
* TemporaryOahSystem#ischemic-heart "% of deaths due to ischemic diseases of the heart"
* TemporaryOahSystem#other-heart "% of deaths due to other diseases of the heart"
* TemporaryOahSystem#other-circulatory-system "% of deaths due to other diseases of the circulatory system"
* TemporaryOahSystem#pneumonia "% of deaths due to Pneumonia"
* TemporaryOahSystem#chronic-lower-respiratory "% of deaths due to chronic diseases of the lower respiratory tract"
